# Simple publish-subscribe example
## Using WifiNINA as communication 
1. Start microros-agent

```ros2 run micro_ros_agent micro_ros_agent udp4 --port 8888```

2. Flash example code

3. Check ros topic

```ros2 topic echo /micro_ros_platformio_node_publisher```
terminal should display a increasing counter send from the microcontroller.

---


## Using Serial communication:
Start microros-agent

```ros2 run micro_ros_agent micro_ros_agent serial --dev /dev/ttyACM0```

uncomment serial-communication codeline in platformio.ini and main.cpp